vote.title: An ordinance amending Ordinance No. 31287, previously approved on August 28, 2019 which abandoned portions of Winnetka Avenue (formerly Earle Street), located near the intersection of Fort Worth and Winnetka Avenues, to Paul V. Toler and Donna Toler and Worth Trinity, LLC, to extend the final replat from one year to 24 months - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
